  "texts": [
    "When a user asks a question, two different search mechanisms are triggered.",
    "Using the ChatGPT API, the question is reduced to a list of relevant keywords in the keyword search method.",
    "These keywords serve as the foundation for searching text-based material by using a free-text search to identify content that corresponds with or matches the keywords that the user originally posed.",
    "In parallel, the OpenAI embeddings API is used to perform a semantic search.",
    "This procedure consists of converting the user's query into a vector representation, which is a format that captures the semantic core of the query."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}